PC application to be used for test and development of the light_node application

Connects to the light_node through the same serial port as used in the real case
by the main node.

In order to be used for development and test the communication protocol needs to
be adapted.

example commands:
control light     - set intensity, color/pattern/behaviour to all, individual or
                  group of lamps...
adjust intensity  - adjust intensity for individual, group or all lights...
set intensity     - set intensity for individual, group or all lights...
set color         - set color for individual, group or all lights...
get intensity
get color
get status
color change      - (start,) stop, time or speed
intensity change  - (start,) stop, time or speed
set global max/stop!?

example structure:
cmd
light id
